<br>
As the slapping footsteps get nearer to where he is they stop suddenly and then the door is knocked on. Poseidon opens his eyes and looks toward the invisisble door. 'ENTER' he says in a commanding voice. It is his servants head that peers in from the bright light of the hall to tell the God he has completed his mission. Poseidon then gives him further instructions. When the guests arrive he is to invite them in to the meeting hall and Poseidon himself will know when they are there. After Poseidon arrives to greet his requested guests the servant is to close all of the doors that lead to and from the room so that the conversation held therein will be kept secret, for none can penetrate into the depths of the sea where Poseidon dwells as none can penetrate into the depths of Hades to find out his secrets. <br>
<br>
